			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				This spell rocks! I use it with my 10th lvl shammy to &quot;blind kite&quot; hehe. I cast a dot on target mob, run back a ways, then cast blind on them and move a step back. The Mob will run around foolishly while soaking DOT damage. When the flash of light wears off, cast annother and re-DOT if needed. Rinse, lather, repeat. Be sure to move back b4 casting flash of light tho, as when the mob runs around looking foolish, it will drag others into the fight. Otherwise this combo works great, have been able to solo yellow and red mobs in this manner,<BR>
<BR>
Halamor 10th season Shaman <BR>
Morell Thule<BR>

				</font>
			</td>

