				Flash of Light can ve a very potent spell if you use it right.  Since it lasts for about 12 seconds, use them at the start of a battle to get a couple DDs off before they regain their sight.  Note that against the AI, if they are already engaged in melee, this spell does nothing.  I love using this spell myself as it looks soooooo funny!
				</font>
