				Still use this as a level 33 shaman. Got it rather late (lev 24 I think in Oasis) but its a blast to use.  I find that it does not get resisted much which I find odd since it is a level one spell.  Effects vary quite a bit.  Sometimes the mob will simply turn around and run for 10-15 seconds and then come back.  Sometimes it will turn 180 degrees over and over for several seconds.   Sometimes it won't go anywhere but it acts like a stun.  Similar to fear though duration is less I think.
